{"tid":1513554,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【首次】新地委中共黨員入董事局 世交胡寶星家族全退","createTime":"2019-08-28T11:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T13:02:36.000Z","uid":68738,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"942375be0b8f8f7ea2ffbfa04c939c213a27206f","tid":1513554,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190828/large/1566986562_6df0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190828%2Flarge%2F1566986562_6df0.jpg&h=207b53ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新地（016）公佈，正式委任前華潤置地（1109）主席兼潤地黨委書記吳向東為新地的獨立非執董，亦為新地歷年來首次有共產黨員加入董事局，9月1日起生效。同時，新地亦宣佈，世交胡寶星爵士將辭任非執行董事，其兒子胡家驃同時終止出任胡寶星爵士之替代董事，兩者均在8月31日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n現年52歲的吳向東，曾出任華潤置地董事會主席及執行董事，並出任潤地黨委書記。由於出任央企黨委書記，先決條件要身為共產黨員，因此，今次也是新地歷來首位共產黨員加入董事局。<br />\n<br />\n文件披露吳向東，持有清華大學建築管理學和工程力學雙學士學位，以及清華大學交通工程碩士學位及三藩市大學工商管理碩士學位。現為華夏幸福基業股 份有限公司之聯席董事長、首席執行官暨總裁。並曾於2009年至2019年二月期間擔任華潤置地的執行董事，並於上述若干期間出任華潤置地的常務副總經理、董事總經理及董事會主席。<br />\n<br />\n有內地傳媒曾報道，吳向東為前華潤置地董事長宋林的心腹，與宋林關係密切，然而在2014年宋林涉嫌嚴重違紀違法，有傳吳向東亦被帶走協助調查，自此在華潤置地的影響力已大不如前。<br />\n<br />\n吳向東自1993年加入潤地，一手締造了華潤萬象城系列，2009年正式進入潤地董事局，2013年更成為潤地主席。但2014年起受集團原董事長、黨委書記宋林「雙規」牽連，辭任華潤置地主席、改任執董，淡出集團核心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190828/59983359\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190828%2F59983359&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5ILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=c7b515c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190828%2F59983359&h=79eace95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190828/59983359</a>"},{"pid":"3d14ef0ff4a8c3fbd78812822e47d80745037a1c","tid":1513554,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd51c6329ea74644d063d0d518a821b3a7bfab72","tid":1513554,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:25:40.000Z","msg":"黨支部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c433fd8152eacea80d7f644b913bd1d9313e9a","tid":1513554,"uid":121562,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd5c4fdae0955301b93369879cd479bae68ef53","tid":1513554,"uid":29620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:28:20.000Z","msg":"加沽"},{"pid":"00b10267cefdfbf584e36a3e30b6dd2bd9f50da8","tid":1513554,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:28:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.28 #Metoo 遮打花園</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.31 民陣遊行 直指中聯辦</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.01 機場 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.02 全港三罷</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚見</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\